                <h4 id="project-name"> SHREDCAST</h4>
                <div id="project-surname">UI / UX Design</div>
                <p>ShredCast is an app that provides Skiers and Snowboarders with customized conditions-based ratings for their favorite mountains. Using weather and conditions data broadcasted by mountain resorts, ShredCast creates a score based on the conditions that matter most to you.</p>
                
                <p> I am currently acting as front-end designer and developer on this project with my friends/partners in crime <a target="blank" href="www.linkedin.com/in/maxskala">Max Skala</a> and <a target="blank" href="http://ezmacdesigns.com/porfolio/index.html">Evan McEldowney</a>. </p>
