    <section class="project">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="large-8 large-offset-2 columns">
                <p>The idea for ShredCast was born from the desire to quickly access weather information from the mountains my buddies and I had a three-mountain season pass to. As early risers and weekend daytrippers, we wanted a way to quickly see which mountain had the best conditions on the day we desired to shred. </p>

                <p>On the lift at Loon the discussion began, "I already have sick name for it, we'll call it ShredCast."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

